<div class="com-share" data-id="6172" data-title="《哎冯导，我们觉得你有些话说得不对》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6172/medium/6172.JPG?1436693724" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6172.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
